---
import { Star } from 'lucide-astro';
---

<section class="py-24 bg-ice dark:bg-dark/50">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-6 lg:px-10">
        <h2 class="text-3xl font-extrabold text-center mb-16 text-dark dark:text-white">Voces Menta</h2>
        <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
            <div class="p-8 bg-white dark:bg-slate-800 rounded-[2.5rem] shadow-sm border border-mint-100 dark:border-slate-700">
                <div class="flex gap-1 mb-4 text-mint-500">
                    <Star class="w-4 h-4 fill-current" /><Star class="w-4 h-4 fill-current" /><Star class="w-4 h-4 fill-current" /><Star class="w-4 h-4 fill-current" /><Star class="w-4 h-4 fill-current" />
                </div>
                <p class="italic text-soft dark:text-mint-100/50 mb-6 text-sm">"Vine por una urgencia y me quedé por la atención. Realmente no sentí nada de dolor. La clínica huele increíblemente bien."</p>
                <div class="flex items-center gap-4">
                    <div class="w-10 h-10 rounded-full bg-mint-100 overflow-hidden">
                        <img src="https://i.pravatar.cc/100?u=1" alt="Sonia R.">
                    </div>
                    <span class="font-bold text-dark dark:text-white text-sm">Sonia R.</span>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="p-8 bg-white dark:bg-slate-800 rounded-[2.5rem] shadow-sm border border-mint-100 dark:border-slate-700">
                <div class="flex gap-1 mb-4 text-mint-500">
                    <Star class="w-4 h-4 fill-current" /><Star class="w-4 h-4 fill-current" /><Star class="w-4 h-4 fill-current" /><Star class="w-4 h-4 fill-current" /><Star class="w-4 h-4 fill-current" />
                </div>
                <p class="italic text-soft dark:text-mint-100/50 mb-6 text-sm">"Mis alineadores Invisalign han cambiado mi sonrisa en meses. El seguimiento digital es súper cómodo para mi agenda."</p>
                <div class="flex items-center gap-4">
                    <div class="w-10 h-10 rounded-full bg-mint-100 overflow-hidden">
                        <img src="https://i.pravatar.cc/100?u=2" alt="Carlos M.">
                    </div>
                    <span class="font-bold text-dark dark:text-white text-sm">Carlos M.</span>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="p-8 bg-white dark:bg-slate-800 rounded-[2.5rem] shadow-sm border border-mint-100 dark:border-slate-700">
                <div class="flex gap-1 mb-4 text-mint-500">
                    <Star class="w-4 h-4 fill-current" /><Star class="w-4 h-4 fill-current" /><Star class="w-4 h-4 fill-current" /><Star class="w-4 h-4 fill-current" /><Star class="w-4 h-4 fill-current" />
                </div>
                <p class="italic text-soft dark:text-mint-100/50 mb-6 text-sm">"Higiene impecable y trato de lujo. No sabía que ir al dentista podía ser una experiencia tan relajante."</p>
                <div class="flex items-center gap-4">
                    <div class="w-10 h-10 rounded-full bg-mint-100 overflow-hidden">
                        <img src="https://i.pravatar.cc/100?u=3" alt="Lucía B.">
                    </div>
                    <span class="font-bold text-dark dark:text-white text-sm">Lucía B.</span>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>
